=== RESEARCH_DATABASE ===
# id: 93
# title: The Research Database
# chinese_title: 研究数据库
# category: Terminal
# mode: dungeon

A research terminal contains petabytes of data — xenobiological surveys, materials science experiments, and linguistic analysis. The database is partially corrupted, but keyword searches still function. What would you like to look up?

* [Search for radical-based technology]
  ~ gain_radical("言")
  "科" (kē) — science, subject, branch
* [Look up local xenobiology data]
  ~ gain_xp(20)
  "生" (shēng) — life, biology
* [Search for valuable material compositions]
  ~ gain_gold(25)
  "据" (jù) — data, evidence, basis
* [Download everything you can]
  ~ gain_item("neural_boost")
  "全" (quán) — complete, whole, all
